Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_inb_chn1

USBN_DMA0_INB_CHN1 = USBN's Inbound DMA for USB0 Channel1

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 writes to L2C via Channel1. Writing of this register sets the base address.
